Use homesick and follow its instructions.

---

homesick clone gustafnk/dotfiles
cd .homesick/repos/dotfiles
git submodule update --init --recursive

---

Also, put these lines in an autostart, if needed:

  # Set Swedish and English keyboard, with shift-alt as keyboard layout toggler
  setxkbmap -layout 'se,us' -option 'grp:alt_shift_toggle' &
  setxkbmap se -option ctrl:nocaps
